sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Bot as Bot
    participant API as Third-Party API
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service

    User->>Bot: Initiate interaction
    Bot->>API: Send request for data
    API-->>Bot: Return data
    Bot->>User: Display data

    User->>Bot: Trigger webhook event
    Bot->>Webhook: Send webhook notification
    Webhook-->>Bot: Acknowledge receipt
    Bot->>User: Confirm webhook event processed